  "texts": [
    "By integrating these two representations, the edge embedding features are generated, which are then employed for the subsequent edge convolution operations within the graph convolutional network block.",
    "This block further consists of two subblocks: one for edge convolution and another for node convolution.",
    "Finally, the output is transformed into a 1D convolutional layer, which employs a linear activation function to produce the final results.",
    "This sophisticated approach by ComplexQA offers a comprehensive evaluation of protein complex structures, enhancing our ability to understand and predict their quality.",
    "In comparative evaluations across diverse datasets, ComplexQA outperformed the other leading algorithms (DProQA, GNN-DOVE, TRScore, GOAP, and ZRANK2)."
